	<h3>VAŽNE OSOBE</h3>
</center>


<center>
	<ul style ="display: inline-block;, text-align: center;" >
		<li>Luka Modrić</li>
		<li>Ronald Galić</li>
		<li>Roditelji</li>
	</ul>
